UPLOAD-AHEAD-CALLBACK is callback for file updates, when uploading
ahead in case `telega-chat-upload-attaches-ahead' is non-nil."
  (if (string-match-p "^https?://" filename)
      (list :@type "inputFileRemote" :id filename)

